---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Home"
  description="GHS pictograms, label builder and visual chemical safety tools for design, logistics and compliance."
>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#062A78] tracking-tight">
      GHS Pictograms
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
      This site is part of the GHS ecosystem: visual tools for hazard pictograms, GHS label design,
      and transport vs workplace marking comparison. Built for designers, logistics teams,
      and anyone who needs clear, compliant chemical hazard communication.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
      More tools and pages will appear here as we build the label constructor and inspector.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
